<H1>Mapping the Business Beat</H1>


<p>By James K. Gentry with help from Donica Mensing. 

<p>Gentry is dean of the School of Journalism at the University of Nevada, Reno, where he runs the Nevada Fellows Program in business reporting. Gentry is the former executive director of the Society of American Business Editors and Writers. 

<p>Mensing is  a doctoral student in the political science program at the University of Nevada, Reno.
