<body bgcolor="#ffffff"> 
<hr noshade size=3>
<center><img src="../../facsnet_grafix/report_tools/covering_business.gif"
alt="Covering Business: "><br>Edited by James K. Gentry, dean, Reynolds School of Journalism, University of Nevada, Reno. 
