Title: Sample letter to motor vehicle bureau
Link: <mailto:pattimcc>; rev="Made"
</DOCHDR>
<html>
<head>
<center>
 <body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<hr noshade size=3>
<img src="http://www.facsnet.org/facsnet_grafix/report_tools/find_em_fast.gif"
alt="Find'Em Fast"><br>By Dave Farrell, investigative reporter for The Detroit News. <BR>Tips on using public information to find (almost) anybody.
 
