</center>

<title>Sample letter to motor vehicle bureau</title>
<H3>REPORTING BASICS</h3>
<h2>Sample letter to motor vehicle bureau</h2>


<hr noshade size=1><address>
 <STRONG>The following sample letter can be used to request driving 
records from state agencies:</STRONG></address><hr noshade size=1>

<p>Your Name Date<br>
Your Street Address<br>
City, State Zip code <p>

Dear Commissioner of Motor Vehicles:<p>
 Please send me all available public information in the driving record of 

JOHN X. DOE. His birthday is 1-2-53. (If you don't have an exact date of 

birth, give an approximate year of birth).
 If your search indicates numerous drivers with the same name, please 
advise me and I will decide which record(s) I wish to purchase.
 Thank you for your help.<p>
    Sincerely,<p>


    Your Name<p>


<br>
<br>
