Title: Footnote
Link: <mailto:pattimcc>; rev="Made"
</DOCHDR>
<html><head><title>Footnote</title></head><body bgcolor="#ffffff"><center><img border=0 src="../../facsnet_grafix/report_tools/sidebar1.gif"
alt="Sidebar: "><h1>Footnote</h1></center><hr><ul><li><strong>Extrapolation:</strong> estimating or inferring something by extending or projecting known information, often by mathematical equations.</ul>
<br>

