 Forensic Packaging Concepts, 7171 Brookwood Valley Circle, Atlanta, GA 
30309<br>
 <b>Phone/Fax</b>: 404-351-0005<br>
 Dr. Rosette has been in the packaging field for more than 12 years, 
marketing and 
designing packages involving every material used in the industry. His 
publications 
include: Improving Tamper Evident Packaging, Technomic Publishing, 1992. 
His 
dissertation was on "Development of an Index for Rating The Effectiveness 
of Tamper-
Evident Packaging Features." He recently released Product Tampering 
Detection, a 
manual designed specifically to assist law enforcement agencies in 
tampering 
investigations.<p>

