<h1><center>Welcome to the<br>
Program for<br>
Agricultural Co-operative Education (PACE)</center></h1>
<br clear="left">
<hr size="10" align="center">
<h3><center>Room 2E10, Agriculture Building<br>
Saskatoon SK  S7N 5A8<br>
Tel:  (306) 966-7766  Fax (306) 966-7788<br>
E-Mail:  PACE@usask.ca<br>
France Bergeron:  Director</h3>
<p>
<center><address><a href="mailto:pace@usask.ca"><img src="im/mail.gif" alt=:[e-mail]"> Send an e-mail to PACE now</a></address><br>
<A HREF="feedback/paceindex.html">Convenient form to request more information or send us your comments.</a></center>
