<title>College of Agriculture - Departments</title>

<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF text=#000000 link=#0000FF vlink=#52188c alink=#ff0000>


<center>
<table border=0 cellpadding=5 cellspacing=5 width=500>
<tr><td align=center valign=middle width="125" rowspan=2><IMG width=120 height=230 border=0 SRC="../im/agric.gif"></td>

<td width="375"><center><font size="+2">College of Agriculture</font><BR>

<font size="+3"><B>Departments</B></font></center>
<p>

<dd>The College's six academic departments, associated research, extension and service units are part of an agriculture science complex which is without compare in Canada.<BR>

<ul><li><font size="+1"><A HREF = "agec.html">
Agricultural Economics</A></font>
<li><font size="+1"><A HREF = "anps.html">
Animal and Poultry Science</A></font>
<li><font size="+1"><A HREF = "amfs.html">
Applied Microbiology and Food Science</A></font>
<li><font size="+1"><A HREF = "http://www.usask.ca/agriculture/cropsci">
Crop Science and Plant Ecology</A></font>
<li><font size="+1"><A HREF = "htsc.html">
Horticulture Science</A></font>
<li><font size="+1"><A HREF = "slsc.html">
Soil Science</A></li></font>

</td></tr></table>
<p>

