<h3><center>Program for Agricultural Co-operative Education (PACE)</center></h3>
<br clear="left">

<hr size="10" align="center">

<p><br><br></p>
<center>[  <a href="http://www.ag.usask.ca/cofa/pace/index.html">PACE Home Page</a>  | <a href="mailto:PACE@usask.ca">Send an e-mail to PACE now</a>]  <br>
