<center><a href="http://www.usask.ca/index.html"><IMG WIDTH=75 HEIGHT=75  SRC="im/uofsLarge.gif"></td><td width="320"></a></center>

<h3><center>Program for Agricultural Co-operative Education (PACE)</center></h3>
<br clear="left">

<p><br><br></p>
<center>[  <a href="http://www.ag.usask.ca/cofa/pace/index.html">PACE Home Page</a>  | <a href="mailto:PACE@usask.ca">Send an e-mail to PACE now</a>  ]</center>
<p><br><br></p>

<hr size="10" align="center">

<h1><center>Greetings from the Prime Minister of Canada</center></h1>
</BLOCKQUOTE> 
<center><a href="http://canada.gc.ca"><IMG SRC="http://canada.gc.ca/images/others/pmsmall.gif" ALT="Picture of Mr. Chretien" WIDTH=117 HEIGHT=150></a></center>
<p><br><br></p>
<p>"I am delighted to extend my warmest greetings to the participants in the Program for Agricultural Co-operative Education (PACE), sponsored by the College of Agriculture of the University of Saskatchewan.</p>

<p>Agriculture has always played an invaluable role not only in Canada's economic prosperity, but also as part of our national heritage.  PACE will be beneficial to students and industry professionals alike, offering them a unique opportunity to invest in the future.  Through discussion and the exchange of ideas, the agricultural sector will play a vital role as mentor to the leaders of tomorrow.  Students will learn the importance of furthering their education and developing the skills that will prepare them to meet the challenges of the path they have chosen to pursue.</p>

<p>Please accept my best wishes for a most successful venture.</p>


<p>Jean Chretien<br>
Prime Minister</p>

<p>Ottawa
1996"</p>   
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<p><br><br></p>
