<TD rowspan=5><p><dd><font size=+1>	Greetings on behalf of the University of Saskatchewan's College of Agriculture Students' Association.  We have been selected this year to run the 1997 Western Association of Agriculture Councils Conference.  To learn more about what WAAC is, and who are some of its participants feel free to browse this page.  For information updates on the upcoming conference check out our <b>HOT NEWS</b> link.</P>
<p><dd>For more information please email us at the link provided below, phone (306) 966-7742 and ask for Jen Warken or Jeff Jackson, or write the following address.  We look forward to seeing WAAC members here in the new year!</p>
<br><center><b>WAAC
<br>51 Campus Drive
<br>Saskatoon, Saskatchewan
<br>CANADA     
<br>S7N 5A8</b></center></font>
