<HEAD><TITLE>SPONSORS</TITLE></HEAD> 

<body bgcolor=#FFFFFF text=#000000 link=#0000FF vlink=#52188c alink=#ff0000>




<center><IMG WIDTH=290 HEIGHT=67  SRC="IM/agchallenges.gif" alt= "Ag-Challenge '96">
<BR>
<BR></center> 


<p>Ag Challenge is an exceptionally successful event. Each year many 
agricultural and local organizations show their support through donations of funds, souvenirs, meals, tours, and various other activities. Without this support Ag-Challenge would not be the success it is. We, as the organizing committee, are very thankful for the sponsorship we receive. The following is a list of those we would like to show special appreciation to. Once again<B> "Thank You to our sponsors for your generous support."</B></P>

<dd><A HREF="http://www.swp.com/">Saskatchewan Wheat Pool</A>
<dd>Sask Energy
<dd>Zeneca Agro
<dd><A HREF="http://www.usask.ca/">University of Saskatchewan</A>
<dd><A HREF="http://www.agrevo.com/">Agrevo</A>
<dd>Agricultural Students' Association (A.S.A.)
<dd><A HREF="http://www.monsanto.com/">Monsanto</A>
<dd>Canadian Seed Growers Association
<dd>Ciba Plant Protection
<dd>DowElanco
<dd>Enviro-Test Laboratories
<dd>Pioneer Hybrid Production Limited
<dd>Saskatchewan Pork International
<dd>Bourgault Industries
<dd>Potash Corporation of Saskatchewan (PCS)
<dd>Highline Manufacturing Incorporated
<dd>Possberg Pork Farms Limited
<dd>John Deere
<dd>Labatt
<dd>SaskTel
<dd>Sherritt
<dd>Saskatchewan Institute of Agrologists
<dd>Saskatchewan Agriculture and Food
<br><br>
