<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000014-B017-77</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://pine.usask.ca:80/cofa/departments/hort/hortinfo/fact/dragonfl.html 128.233.59.24 19970101085729 text/html 2878
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
