<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000014-B018-163</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://pine.usask.ca:80/cofa/departments/hort/hortinfo/fact/powdery.html 128.233.59.24 19970101090329 text/html 4385
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
