<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000014-B019-43</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://pine.usask.ca:80/cofa/departments/hort/hortinfo/fact/birch.html 128.233.59.24 19970101090552 text/html 3135
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
