<DOCNO>WT24-B02-138</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000014-B019-57</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://pine.usask.ca:80/cofa/departments/hort/hortinfo/fact/mosquito.html 128.233.59.24 19970101090602 text/html 5549
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
