<DOCNO>WT24-B02-160</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000014-B021-126</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://pine.usask.ca:80/cofa/departments/hort/hortinfo/pests/n_scale.html 128.233.59.24 19970101091033 text/html 4377
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
