<DOCNO>WT24-B02-220</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000014-B026-107</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://pine.usask.ca:80/cofa/departments/hort/hortinfo/plants/passion.html 128.233.59.24 19970101092305 text/html 5045
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
