<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000014-B026-267</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://pine.usask.ca:80/cofa/departments/hort/hortinfo/plants/x-mas.html 128.233.59.24 19970101092443 text/html 3797
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
