<DOCNO>WT24-B02-300</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000015-B014-169</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://pine.usask.ca:80/cofa/departments/hort/hortinfo/yards/fairy1.html 128.233.59.24 19970101094318 text/html 8617
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
