<DOCNO>WT24-B02-330</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000015-B016-128</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://pine.usask.ca:80/cofa/departments/hort/hortinfo/fruit/cherry.html 128.233.59.24 19970101095047 text/html 16059
